VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Supabase dashboard setup (required for auth emails & phone OTP):
# 1. Authentication → URL Configuration → Redirect URLs:
#    - http://localhost:5173/auth/callback
#    - https://your-domain.com/auth/callback
# 2. Authentication → Providers → Email: enable Confirm email
# 3. Authentication → Providers → Phone: enable and configure SMS (Twilio/MessageBird)
# 4. For reliable email delivery, configure SMTP under Authentication → Email
